Class HDBManager

Object
User
HDBManager
public class HDBManager extends User
Represents an HDB Manager who can create and manage BTO projects. Managers have the authority to approve or reject applications and officer registrations.
Since:
2025-03-16
Version:
1.0
Author:
SC2002 G Team
